content.html: I've deleted a bunch of tweets. There's likely a better outlet for all the messages I've received than my twitter account, and everything I've heard about blackmail and lawsuits is doing a number on my anxiety levels. Sorry folks. Not forgotten. Still angry. Just need a break.
